author: itv.com
title: Jersey's international popstar
text:
Jersey has its very own international popstar who has just released a new book.
16-year-old Tallia Storm was discovered by Elton John and has performed around the world.
Her book, Pop Girl, is based on her experiences.
The young star moved to Jersey a year ago and performed at the 'Big Gig in the Park' event in July.
She will be live in our studio at 6pm tonight.
Watch her debut EP below.
Last updated Tue 13 Oct 2015 Entertainment Jersey
